queries.sql: SELECT YEAR(tanggal) as tahun, MONTHNAME(tanggal) as bulan, sum(saldomasuk) as sum FROM `transfer` WHERE month(tanggal) = month(CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY `tahun`, `bulan` ORDER BY `tahun` DESC LIMIT 1

SELECT YEAR(tanggal) as tahun, MONTHNAME(tanggal) as bulan, sum(saldomasuk) as sum, `rekening` FROM `transfer` WHERE month(tanggal) = month(CURRENT_DATE) AND YEAR(tanggal) = 2024 GROUP BY `rekening`, `tahun`, `bulan` ORDER BY `tahun` DESC
SELECT YEAR(tanggal) as tahun, `tanggal`, sum(saldomasuk) as sum FROM `transfer` WHERE month(tanggal) = month(CURRENT_DATE) AND YEAR(tanggal) = 2024 GROUP BY `tahun` ORDER BY `tahun` DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT YEAR(tanggal) as tahun, `tanggal`, sum(saldomasuk) as sum FROM `transfer` WHERE month(tanggal) = month(CURRENT_DATE) - 1 AND YEAR(tanggal) = 2024 GROUP BY `tahun` ORDER BY `tahun` DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT YEAR(tanggal) as tahun, `tanggal`, sum(saldomasuk) as sum FROM `transfer` WHERE month(tanggal) = month(CURRENT_DATE) - 2 AND YEAR(tanggal) = 2024 GROUP BY `tahun` ORDER BY `tahun` DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT *, sum(tunggakandu) as tungdu, sum(tunggakantl) as tungtl, sum(tunggakanspp) as tungspp FROM `santri` WHERE `program` = 'mandiri' AND `kelas` != 'keluar'
SELECT *, sum(tunggakandu) as tungdu, sum(tunggakantl) as tungtl FROM `santri` WHERE `program` = 'beasiswa' AND `kelas` != 'keluar'
